  <entry>
    <title>为什么版权越来越规矩，歌曲却越来越不火了</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2025/01/26/%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E7%89%88%E6%9D%83%E8%B6%8A%E6%9D%A5%E8%B6%8A%E8%A7%84%E7%9F%A9%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%8C%E6%9B%B2%E5%8D%B4%E8%B6%8A%E6%9D%A5%E8%B6%8A%E4%B8%8D%E7%81%AB%E4%BA%86/"/>
